PATTERN JOKES

pattern_jokes recognizes "jokes" used where "yokes" or "okay" was meant
sometimes a fast typist's keystroke registers an unintended J at the start
this pattern looks for the substitution in context

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_jokes:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan for "jokes" in contexts that do not match its expected meaning

VERB correct
substitute the contextually likely word silently
